description:
This is a 15 minute workout called 'Time Is Of The Essence | 15 Min Quick Indoor Cycling HIIT' from the channel GCN Training.
The workout falls under Cardio/Indoor biking and Cardio/HIIT.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Beginner fitness levels.
You'll need Exercise Bike for this workout.
The workout has a The Firestarter and The Warrior Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Challenging and Moderate.

Original workout description: Manon and her team bring us an efficient cycling workout that will work you hard in a manageable time. Getting increasingly harder this workout has short sharp efforts with time in between for recovery. This is going to be a sweaty one, even if it is just 15 minutes long!
